info:
  title: BrAPI
  version: ''
openapi: 3.0.0
paths: {}
components:
  parameters:
    page:
      description: |- 
        Used to request a specific page of data to be returned.
        
        The page indexing starts at 0 (the first page is 'page'= 0). Default is `0`.
      example: '0'
      in: query
      name: page
      required: false
      schema:
        type: integer
